---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Subscribe from '../components/Subscribe.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About | Cyber-Brief"
  description="Cyber-Brief is written by Van Munoz, founder of Cyber Edge LLC and a practitioner with over 25 years leading information security initiatives across financial services."
>
  <Nav />

  <div class="page">
    <div class="about-wrap">

      <div class="page-header">
        <div class="page-eyebrow">
          <div class="eyebrow-line"></div>
          <span class="eyebrow-text">About</span>
        </div>
        <h1>Cyber intelligence for financial service leaders.</h1>
        <p>Cyber-Brief exists for the CISOs, executives, and board members who need to stay ahead of the governance, risk management, and compliance landscape.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="about-body">
        <div class="about-text">
          <p>Every issue is verified, sourced, and written for decision-makers. We translate what's happening in cyber governance into what it means for your organization, your exposure, and your next conversation with the board.</p>

          <h2>Who's behind it</h2>
          <p>Cyber-Brief is written by Van Munoz, founder of Cyber Edge LLC and a practitioner with over 25 years leading information security initiatives across financial services, insurance, and critical infrastructure.</p>
          <p>He's worked alongside the leadership teams making these decisions — navigating regulatory frameworks, guiding organizations through audits, and helping translate risk into terms that drive action.</p>

          <h2>The mission</h2>
          <p>Most cybersecurity content is written for practitioners. Cyber-Brief is written for the people those practitioners report to — executives and board members who need high-signal intelligence without the technical noise.</p>
          <p>Every brief is built around a single question: <strong>what does this mean for your organization?</strong></p>
        </div>

        <div class="about-profile">
          <div class="profile-image">
            <img src="/img/cyber-edge-profile.png" alt="Van Munoz — Cyber Edge LLC" />
          </div>
          <div class="profile-card">
            <div class="profile-name">Van Munoz</div>
            <div class="profile-title">Founder, Cyber Edge LLC</div>
            <div class="profile-divider"></div>
            <ul class="profile-credentials">
              <li>25+ years in information security</li>
              <li>Financial services & insurance</li>
              <li>Critical infrastructure</li>
              <li>Regulatory frameworks & audits</li>
              <li>Board-level risk communication</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

  <Subscribe />
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .about-wrap {
    padding-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .page-header {
    padding: 80px 0 56px;
    max-width: 680px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 64px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .page-eyebrow {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .eyebrow-line {
    width: 28px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--coral);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .eyebrow-text {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.16em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--coral);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 48px;
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--heading);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .page-header p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--body-text);
    line-height: 1.75;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .about-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 320px;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading);
    margin: 40px 0 16px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .about-text p {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--body-text);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .about-text strong {
    color: var(--heading);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-profile {
    position: sticky;
    top: 88px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  .profile-image {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 1/1;
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-bright);
    background: var(--bg3);
    transition: border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .profile-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .profile-card {
    background: var(--bg2);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 24px;
    transition: background 0.3s, border-color 0.3s;
  }

  .profile-name {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--heading);
    margin-bottom: 4px;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .profile-title {
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--coral);
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .profile-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }

  .profile-credentials {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .profile-credentials li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--body-text);
    padding-left: 16px;
    position: relative;
    transition: color 0.3s;
  }

  .profile-credentials li::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 10px;
    width: 5px;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--coral);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 40px;
    }

    .about-profile {
      position: static;
    }

    .profile-image {
      aspect-ratio: 3/2;
    }
  }
</style>
